a diversity in the virome composition between the collected sample types which also represent different potential shedding routes for the detected viruses. At the same time, several novel viruses represent first reports of these pathogens from bats in Sri Lanka. The detection of two different coronaviruses in the samples indicates the potential general persistence of this virus species in\n              M.\n              \u00a0\n              phillipsi\n              bats. Based on phylogenetics, the identified viruses are closely related to bat-associated viruses with comparably low estimation of human pathogenic potential. In further studies, the seasonal variation of the virome will be analyzed to identify possible shedding patterns for particular viruses.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Muzeniek, Therese", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Perera, Thejanee", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Siriwardana, Sahan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bas, Dilara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bayram, Fatimanur", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "\u00d6ruc, Mizgin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Becker-Ziaja, Beate", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Perera, Inoka", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Weerasena, Jagathpriya", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Handunnetti, Shiroma", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schwarz, Franziska", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Premawansa, Gayani", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Premawansa, Sunil", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yapa, Wipula", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nitsche, Andreas", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kohl, Claudia", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/25259c9574f63c99744ce2726352ce07", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/2641a03f85aeb0f4a326295915ea0b714c0de69126baebb6bd88333eb3d413ac", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "u